title: Designer Skin Body Bronzer, Ruby, 13.5 Fluid Ounce
description: Prepare yourself for a fantastical sensory experience. Feel the heat of our ruby infused tingle, intertwined with spicy capsaicin fruit. Just when you think you can't handle the heat. Refreshing emerald cooling essence with licorice extract soothes skin, leaving behind the darkest shade of bronze imaginable. No magical slippers required. Fragrance: fresh camu camu
